Package edu.sdsc.mmtf.spark.datasets

Classes that create or manipulate Spark Datasets.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CustomReportService
    This class uses RCSB PDB Tabular Report RESTful web services to retrieve metadata and annotations for all current entries in the Protein Data Bank.
    GroupInteractionExtractor
    Creates a dataset of interactions of a specified group within a cutoff distance.
    PolymerSequenceExtractor
    Creates a dataset of polymer sequences using the full sequence used in the experiment (i.e., the "SEQRES" record in PDB files).
    SecondaryStructureExtractor
    Creates a dataset of 3-state secondary structure (alpha, beta, coil) derived from the DSSP secondary structure assignment.
